asynchronous for-each and reduce operations using C++11

I started with my own ugly implementation that used to be in the Hydrodynamics project.
I then moved it into here, made it a singleton to let it persist and give it a thread pool.
Then I started stealing bits and pieces from:
http://progsch.net/wordpress/?p=81

currently depends on GLApp solely for the Makefile.mk
... some day I'll put that and the include/Common folder in a project of its own so things don't have to build against OpenGL and SDL if they don't need to
